    • Method Detail

      • getHeaderRow

        java.lang.String[] getHeaderRow()
                         throws AnaplanAPIException,
                                java.io.IOException
        Return the header row. This may be called multiple times, but will return the same value.
        Returns:
        If there is no header information available, then null; otherwise, an array of string header values, one per column.
        Throws:
        AnaplanAPIException
        java.io.IOException

      • readDataRow

        java.lang.String[] readDataRow()
                        throws AnaplanAPIException,
                               java.io.IOException
        Read and return the next row of data.
        Returns:
        If there is no more data to be read, then null; otherwise, an array of string cell values, one per column.
        Throws:
        AnaplanAPIException
        java.io.IOException
